The Golden Bear and the two winners of the acting awards from this year's Berlinale, the award for directing and the jury award from Cannes and much more will present the 6th year of festival film from Berlin, Venice and Cannes. This year, the Be2Can festival will bring a selection of the most remarkable and inspiring things presented by the competitions of the three most important European film festivals.
