"That's why we found him relatively quickly. However, if he had the Záchranka application on his phone, our rescuers would certainly have reached him sooner, and at the same time, the 155 dispatching centre would have immediately known about the accident and his situation," noted Radan Jaškovský.
He added that a charged mobile phone with the Záchranka application activated should be a matter of course in the mountains today.
