Strawberry, plum and invisible. Choose the right shade of lipstick: There is more than one red
When choosing a red lipstick, you should first determine whether you are a warm or cold type. Try a simple test - look at the veins on your wrist. If they are blue, you are a cold type, if they are green, then you are a warm type. When choosing a new red lipstick, first of all, put it on the distribution based on the undertone. Only in the next, consider the texture.
If you are a woman with a cold undertone, then purple, plum, cherry or mauve lipsticks are suitable for you.
If you fall into the warm skin tone category, choose such lipsticks. You can recognize them by the fact that they tend to orange, coral, gold or brown reflections.
It may happen to you that some veins look green and others blue. In that case, congratulate yourself - you don't have to look at the undertone and you can focus only on your color preferences.
