For anyone who is planning to travel abroad, travel insurance should be a matter of course. Thanks to the possibility of arranging it and paying by card online, it can be done even at the last minute. However, the mere possession of a payment card often means insurance protection when travelling. "For example, with embossed MasterCard Gold and MasterCard Business cards, travel insurance is an integral part of foreign travel to all countries of the world. Holders of these cards can also insure their family with whom they are travelling. They often do not need any other arrangements," adds Kateřina Petko from Expobank CZ. However, it is always advisable to check the scope of the insurance, i.e. whether it covers all activities that travellers plan to undertake.
