Mahulena Bočanová interrupted her one-year detox and is sinning again!
More than a year ago, Mahulena Bočanová confided in Blesk that she had given up alcohol. "During the holidays, I said to myself that I would give my old, exhausted fifty-year-old body a breather. I gave myself a deadline forever. I feel very relaxed, I have a lot of energy and, most importantly, my psyche has improved. Lately, I have not been well mentally. I wake up better, I do not have a headache, I have more energy and money."
A year of abstinence was enough and the actress found her way back to alcohol. "Sometimes I drink bubbles or quality wine, but I don't drink what I used to. I have one glass and I have fun until the morning. I have a bottle of wine in the fridge for a week. I also liked the non-alcoholic beer, which I can drink at any time," said Mahulena, who is still a couple with Brno entrepreneur Petr.
After the holidays, Bočanová also returned to the theatre season and will start in the series "The Rose Garden Surgery." "I'm ashamed of the first two performances, I was really bad, I was slurring my words. But it's getting better," the actress smiles critically.
